## Sheet 11: Financial Formulas & Calculations
### Key Financial Formulas (Copy these to your calculations)
```
Current Ratio = Current Assets / Current Liabilities
Quick Ratio = (Current Assets - Inventory) / Current Liabilities
Debt-to-Equity = Total Debt / Total Equity
ROE = Net Income / Shareholders' Equity
ROA = Net Income / Total Assets
Gross Margin = (Revenue - COGS) / Revenue
Net Margin = Net Income / Revenue
Working Capital = Current Assets - Current Liabilities
Cash Conversion Cycle = DSO + DIO - DPO
Interest Coverage = EBIT / Interest Expense
```

### Excel Formulas for Automation
```
Status Count: =COUNTIF(Status_Column,"Completed")
Completion %: =COUNTIF(Status_Column,"Completed")/COUNTA(Status_Column)
Budget Variance: =Actual_Amount - Budget_Amount
Variance %: =(Actual_Amount - Budget_Amount)/Budget_Amount
Days Overdue: =IF(Due_Date<TODAY(),TODAY()-Due_Date,0)
Risk Score: =Probability * Impact
```

